{"id": "GB-024", "role": "cyber", "type": "answerable", "query": "Name one approved cipher suite.", "answer": "- One approved cipher suite is **TLS_DHE_DSS_WITH_3DES_EDE_CBC_SHA**. This cipher suite is mandated by RFC 2246 for IPP Printers that support Transport Layer Security (TLS) for server authentication and operation privacy (Source 4).\n\n- Additionally, the same cipher suite, **TLS_DHE_DSS_WITH_3DES_EDE_CBC_SHA**, is required for implementations of the STARTTLS extension for IMAP, POP3, and ACAP to ensure interoperability between compliant implementations (Source 9).", "sources": [{"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\system_administrator_docs\\rfc_standards\\rfc2246.txt", "chunks": 2, "avg_relevance": 0.8149068322698669, "access_tags": ["shared"], "access_tag_source": "default_document_tags"}, {"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\system_administrator_docs\\rfc_standards\\rfc2566.txt", "chunks": 2, "avg_relevance": 0.8852179389040351, "access_tags": ["shared"], "access_tag_source": "default_document_tags"}, {"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\system_administrator_docs\\rfc_standards\\rfc2910.txt", "chunks": 1, "avg_relevance": 0.8732900934077021, "access_tags": ["shared"], "access_tag_source": "default_document_tags"}, {"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\cyber_security_docs\\Ethical Hacker_s Penetration Testing Guide_ Vulnerability Assessment and Attack Simulation on Web, Mobile, Network Services and Wireless Networks.pdf", "chunks": 3, "avg_relevance": 0.6999088939284203, "access_tags": ["shared"], "access_tag_source": "default_document_tags"}, {"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\system_administrator_docs\\rfc_standards\\rfc2595.txt", "chunks": 1, "avg_relevance": 0.6667388131574806, "access_tags": ["shared"], "access_tag_source": "default_document_tags"}, {"path": "C:\\HybridRAG3_Educational\\data\\source\\mixed\\internet-security-cryptographic-principles-algorithms-protocols-m.-rh